projects.title: Graph Visualizer
projects.description:
It is a Graph Visualizer created in Java in which one can create custom graphs and visualize BFS, DFS, Dijkstra, Components, Spanning Tree, Bridges, and Articulation point.
We won First Prize in DSA Mini Project in Second Year with this Project.

projects.title: LookUp
projects.description: It was a PBL project in the First Year, This project was a custom notification app where teachers can post assignments, news, and instructions, and students were notified using Gmail. It had active 100 users when Online Classes were going.

projects.title: Unity Game
projects.description:
A Third Person Shooter Game created using Unity.
This project was created for the CG subject in Third Semester and it won First Prize in CG mini project.

projects.title: Sudoku
projects.description:
A Full Featured Sudoku Game. Features of Sudoku: Hard Mode, Hints, Auto Solve, Danger Indication and Animations.
Was Created as a Case Study for Discrete Maths

projects.title: Typing Multiplayer
projects.description: A Website which can be used to host Typing Games and Chat with Friends and one can also Join other Groups and spend fun times with other and compare speeds using charts and learn typing.

projects.title: Django Blog
projects.description: A Full Featured Django Blog with Markdown support. This Project has User and Admin Authentication and users can comment on blogs and others comments.

projects.title: Maze Generator
projects.description: A Maze-Generator using DFS Algorithm which can be used to generate mazes and also get the solution of the generated mazes.
